reviewText: it was a good buy. it was what i was looking for. i was very happy.
I loved every minute of this. A couple of guys had there's before i got mine and they all raved about the discs they have. I plan on buying more soon!!!

These are the discs that are possibly in a lawsuit?? They aren't worth the high price I paid for them!! Waiting all these years for Classic Memphis footage and this is what I get? My husband's VHS tapes look better than this. Sad.
